    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Narrow strips of land connecting two larger land masses separated by the sea, such as the Isthmus of Panama.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
